---
config:
  theme: base
  themeVariables:
    background: "#ffffff"
    fontFamily: "Arial"
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User
    participant API
    participant Queue
    participant Worker
    participant Store

    User->>+API: Submit command
    API->>Store: Persist desired state
    Store-->>API: Saved
    API-)Queue: Dispatch work item
    API-->>-User: Accepted

    Queue-)Worker: Deliver work item
    Worker->>Store: Read desired state
    Store-->>Worker: Current state

    alt Apply succeeds
        Worker->>Store: Write result
        Store-->>Worker: Updated
    else Transient conflict
        loop Bounded retry
            Worker->>Store: Re-read and retry update
            Store-->>Worker: Current state or success
        end
    end

    Note over API,Store: Replace this note with the real state owner and retry invariant.

